  "title": "PLC Engineer (Power System)",
  "description": "<h2>PLC Engineer (Power System)</h2>\n<p><strong>Visit www.ppsjob.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>Handle application programme development &amp; change management, deployment management &amp; documentation.</p>\n<p>Implantation of PLC/SCADA project from concept to design and programming.</p>\n<p>Interface with SCADA &amp; PLC programming</p>\n<p>Capable of performing troubleshooting independently.</p>\n<p>Coordinate and manage factory testing in both company premises and customerâs site.</p>\n<p>Responsible for integration of both hardware &amp; software work as well as implementation</p>\n<p>Carry out proper execution of the integration/engineering/maintenance work.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Qualifications:</p>\n<p>At least Diploma/Degree in Electrical/Electronic or related discipline</p>\n<p>With at least 3-5 years of experience in PLC.</p>\n<p>Familiar with Safety PLC programming.</p>\n<p>Familiar with Siemens and Schneider PLCs.</p>\n<p>Able to read and interpret electrical schematics, plans, drawing etc.</p>\n<p>Able to work under pressure, multi task and good coordination of tasks</p>\n<p>Good interpersonal skills, able to work both independently and in teams</p>\n<p><br></p>",
